metadata.name: Warrior Crox ????
metadata.description: Warrior Crox is a unique and limited NFT collection consisting of a total of 10 000 Crox, however they are all separated into 4 different generations of Crox. Each one of the Crox is a true warrior and some generations of the Crox have weapons of some kind. They are all rare, however, some have rarer traits than others. We have also created Warrior Crox Comics that you can read for free. Visit our official website, you can find all useful information you seek for there www.warriorcrox.com .
